5. Kong Core Concepts
Service

Represents backend API.

Example:

service:
  name: user-service
  url: http://localhost:3001
Route

Defines path exposed to users.

route:
  path: /users

Flow:

Client hits /users
Kong forwards to user-service
Consumer

Represents API user/client/app.

Used in:

API keys
ACL
Authentication
Plugin

Adds features.

Examples:

rate-limiting
key-auth
basic-auth
cors
prometheus